body:
Reproducer :

```systemverilog
typedef enum bit [2:0] {
    ENUM_VAL = 3'b110
} enumtype;

typedef struct packed {
    enumtype t;
} sbus_t;

module test_top();

    sbus_t sig;

    initial
    begin
        sig.t = ENUM_VAL;
        $display("%d %d %d", sig.t[2], sig.t[1], sig.t[0]);
    end

endmodule
```

```
$ iverilog -g2012 ../test.sv -o test && ./test
6 6 6
```

Running in `xsim` shows `1 1 0` which is what I'd expect.

